<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

24:13.722 --> 24:16.527
<i>♪ In the quiet way ♪</i>

24:16.639 --> 24:19.418
<i>♪ You caught my eye ♪</i>

24:19.673 --> 24:22.189
<i>♪ Oh ♪</i>

24:22.356 --> 24:27.165
<i>♪ Caught enough to get you memorized ♪</i>

