36:39.106 --> 36:42.466
<i>♪ And I'd have never known ♪</i>

36:42.554 --> 36:43.705
<i>♪ Oh, the glory ♪</i>

36:43.793 --> 36:46.067
<i>♪ Of it all ♪</i>

36:47.472 --> 36:49.530
<i>♪ Was lost on me ♪</i>

36:50.104 --> 36:54.805
<i>♪ Till I saw how hard
it'd be to reach you ♪</i>

36:55.313 --> 36:59.620
<i>♪ And I would always be
light-years ♪</i>

36:59.747 --> 37:03.497
<i>♪ Light-years away from you ♪</i>

37:05.261 --> 37:07.176
<i>♪ Light-years ♪</i>

37:07.398 --> 37:11.299
<i>♪ Light-years away from you. ♪</i>

37:32.058 --> 37:34.272
What, you feeling your age,
old man?

