37:47.650 --> 37:49.250
Responsibility.

37:51.125 --> 37:53.658
For me, it was always
a pain in the ass word.

37:54.913 --> 37:56.654
When I was young,
it meant doing chores.

37:56.741 --> 37:58.504
As I got older,
it meant not getting to do

37:58.592 --> 38:00.054
the stuff I really wanted to do.

38:01.540 --> 38:03.807
I was going down a wrong path
in my 20s.

38:08.226 --> 38:10.003
Then your mom got pregnant.

38:11.912 --> 38:13.320
And being responsible,

38:13.652 --> 38:15.657
setting the right example
for you,

38:16.614 --> 38:18.084
it saved me.

38:19.300 --> 38:20.262
That's when I realized

38:20.349 --> 38:23.153
"responsibility" didn't have
to be a pain in the ass word.

38:26.365 --> 38:27.469
Son.

38:28.166 --> 38:29.532
Hey.

38:31.796 --> 38:33.563
Don't even think about it.

38:36.382 --> 38:37.724
A'ight?

38:41.157 --> 38:42.584
Yeah.

38:43.436 --> 38:44.671
A'ight.

38:46.481 --> 38:47.775
I'll watch the baby.

38:47.863 --> 38:49.372
