that have barbecues,

38:59.620 --> 39:03.156
and, on occasion,
your wonderful father...

39:03.959 --> 39:05.595
I'm down to babysit.

39:06.327 --> 39:08.400
Get some QT
with my granddaughter.

39:09.090 --> 39:10.510
W-Wait, are you sure?

39:10.783 --> 39:12.563
You're making
breakfast tomorrow.

39:12.763 --> 39:14.740
And you better not half-ass it,
either.

39:14.842 --> 39:16.209
I want the full deal.

39:16.480 --> 39:18.252
Western omelets
and hash browns.

39:18.419 --> 39:20.421
- Yeah? All right.
- Yeah, okay. Okay.

39:20.509 --> 39:21.821
Yeah.

39:26.707 --> 39:28.589
I used to sing here
all the time,

39:28.677 --> 39:31.512
and they basically paid me
in burgers.

