39:45.559 --> 39:46.640
No, no, no, I'm okay.

39:46.728 --> 39:48.260
- We're actually just gonna...
- Yes.

39:48.777 --> 39:50.626
It's-it's been a day.

39:50.760 --> 39:53.241
