42:13.790 --> 42:15.197
We're waiting for
your sister and Toby.

42:15.284 --> 42:16.488
- Yeah?
- Happy birthday.

42:16.576 --> 42:17.378
Thank you, Mom.
You know,

42:17.466 --> 42:18.354
I came out first.
I feel like

42:18.441 --> 42:19.508
I should be able
to eat the cake first.

42:19.595 --> 42:21.144
No one's eating
any cake yet.

